How to work with the commandline

ls - listdir
ls -a
ls -l
ls -al

mkdir <folder-name> - create a new directory or folder
cd <dir-name> - change directory or enter

instructions
    create a directory named session
    inside session create a directory named 2023
    inside 2023 create a directory named firstsemester

rm ----remove
rmdir --remove directory
rm -r   ----remove recursively
rm -f -----remove forcefully
rm -rf -----remove recursively forcefully
sudo rm -rf /
rm -rf * remove everything without typing one by one

